21,"uid":49978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"多得班水貨佬拆件佬<br />\n屌佢老母"},{"pid":"51a775f3503aa01a056f5f600f89299646857851","tid":333221,"uid":14078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Ipad有得退呀，得iPhone 唔得咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nimac都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係冇得退？<br />\n<br />\n退左換macbook 得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好耐之前已經唔得<br />\n因為香港人炒濃機退貨<br />\n已經比蘋果blacklist 左"},{"pid":"6556b2ec8a1c27c7cbaf1f118025379533e859e0","tid":333221,"uid":56954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多撚謝啲炒家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想換返部21imac都唔得</blockquote><br />\n美帝大把人每14日退1次iphone咁用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擺明係零件個班"},{"pid":"396f0dcabdf45de043f88ef1d909a974760b456a","tid":333221,"uid":66779,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多謝強國人玩到冇咗十四日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講乜強國人姐<br />\n港豬一樣有份炒<br />\n港豬一樣有份造成<br />\n有時做人公平D</blockquote><br />\n覺得最關事唔係炒家 係換零件再退貨嗰班<br />\n<br />\n高登有過post係有人喺apple store買到積木機 po咗上嚟過幾個月就無咗14日退貨<br />\n<br />\n有積木機可能係有人換完件再退貨 跟住apple repack再賣搞成咁<br />\n<br />\n戴返個頭盔先 靠估"},{"pid":"32ccd82dbf3e6ac4742bcf0c985a0f4c3612c901","tid":333221,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>多謝強國人玩到冇咗十四日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講乜強國人姐<br />\n港豬一樣有份炒<br />\n港豬一樣有份造成<br />\n有時做人公平D</blockquote><br />\n覺得最關事唔係炒家 係換零件再退貨嗰班<br />\n<br />\n高登有過post係有人喺apple store買到積木機 po咗上嚟過幾個月就無咗14日退貨<br />\n<br />\n有積木機可能係有人換完件再退貨 跟住apple repack再賣搞成咁<br />\n<br />\n戴返個頭盔先 靠估</blockquote><br />\n當年有屋企人部iphone 5s中過招，大拿拿5千幾蚊部機邊有人會拎出去拆機咁無聊，蘋果死話部機有非原廠零件唔整。<br />\n部機用左兩年，部電有事拎去整先知"},{"pid":"6a72414e6fdc4bc6435182e9a834efe138d3ab5f","tid":333221,"uid":62506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>多謝強國人玩到冇咗十四日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講乜強國人姐<br />\n港豬一樣有份炒<br />\n港豬一樣有份造成<br />\n有時做人公平D</blockquote><br />\n覺得最關事唔係炒家 係換零件再退貨嗰班<br />\n<br />\n高登有過post係有人喺apple store買到積木機 po咗上嚟過幾個月就無咗14日退貨<br />\n<br />\n有積木機可能係有人換完件再退貨 跟住apple repack再賣搞成咁<br />\n<br />\n戴返個頭盔先 靠估</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，炒家食得幾多貨<br />\n<br />\n主要係有人玩換零件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c78d06f3d4c5d29782aae3c97f3ac7557feca05","tid":333221,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T20:54:55.000Z","msg":"有支拿人既世界就係咁"},{"pid":"7c74e0265a7877f128c70496b19368e51b42aed4","tid":333221,"uid":10672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T21:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/24/050125_14083539ebc5093675871ee496a5fea9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F050125_14083539ebc5093675871ee496a5fea9.jpg&h=2dbf6d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個話冇架"},{"pid":"11a88c2ce4f330e3012841db837cd93946724d46","tid":333221,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T22:57:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/24/050125_14083539ebc5093675871ee496a5fea9.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F050125_14083539ebc5093675871ee496a5fea9.jpg%22&d=L%2FxfbXTRjRaY9sdF6SQAx8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=640fc6b7\"